1. Go into autoconf and launch AUtoRege.sh (LLVM source is on Ubuntu /usr/src/llvm-3.1/llvm-3.1)
2. Run the configure script (./configure --with-llvm-config=llvm-config). Works only on Linux
3. Go into the KermetaGC folder and run make
4. Generate the IR code (from the folder example): llc -load ../Release+Asserts/lib/KermetaGC.so sample.ll
